In re Resignation of Zaller.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Zaller (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1212.]

(No. 91-2284 Submitted December 4, 1991 Decided December 11, 1991.)

The resignation of Edmund John Zaller as an attorney, Registration No. 0023934, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
